日，卫龙回应红星资本局称，系国家间标准不一样，产品符合中国标准，安全合规，消费者可放心食用。对于亲嘴烧后续能否在日本售卖的问题，卫龙表示按照日本标准调整配方就可以。 根据公告，90 箱卫龙亲嘴烧经典香辣风味（每箱净含量 480g）被召回，原因为产品被检测到日本当地食品卫生法中不允许使用的食品添加剂 TBHQ，含量为 0.005g/kg。公告显示，召回的产品保质期 5 个月，生产日期为 2024 年 5 月 7 日以后，销售日期为 5 月 21 日至 8 月 23 日。 卫龙回应亲嘴烧在日本被召回：国家间标准不一，产品符合中国标准"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-29026f30461cc043d925f87d55a9c817_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "25 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/1075360044"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI7M/Kkt3w9FoQAxoJMTExMTkxODI5IL+xvrgGMAA4uAVAD3IKMTA3NTM2MDA0NHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "16_1729405788.646084", "card_id": "Q_784234818", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 190}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如果人类在地球上挖出一个万米深坑，在里面放置几千枚核弹，同时引爆，反复操作，能把地球炸开吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "反复在同一个地点操作，能挖多深就挖多深，能放置多少核弹就放置多少核弹，炸完一次又一次，能把地球撕开两半吗？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-ee23ee85ea2922bb73bace2b3d28bf79_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "22 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/784234818"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I7M/Kkt3w9FoQAxoJMTExMDE5NTg3IO2JlbgGMAA4nQNAEHIJNzg0MjM0ODE4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "17_1729405788.646464", "card_id": "Q_757390154", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 230}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "你觉得是人性本善，还是人性本恶？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "人天生是魔鬼还是天使？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-37641b1760c0dcf95d5d245328eda237_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "14 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#